results.name: A rearrangement of the terms of A027746 (seen as flat list) such that adjacent terms are distinct.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
program: f u [] w x = f 1 (reverse $ a027746_row' (u * x)) w (x + 1)
f u (v:vs) w x | v == w    = f (u * v) vs w x
| otherwise = v : f u vs v x
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Dec 01 2015
